      "content": "You could use terms like \"impact on team cohesion\" or \"maintaining constructive discourse\" to address the issue professionally. Phrases such as \"needs to foster a more collaborative environment\" or \"ensure contributions enhance team morale\" focus on the *result* of their actions. This frames the concern around team effectiveness rather than personal failings. Remember, always tie the feedback back to business outcomes.",
